  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘晨"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘晨上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蟾宫摘桂高仙手，独占鳌头天下知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙家寂静洞门闭，鹤伴孤云去复还。只有桃花留不住，跟随流水到人间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官刘晨，当年与兄弟同伴，上京赴试。蒙主龙恩，钦点文武状元。绕道还乡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行至天台山游玩山景，被猛虎冲散。多亏麻姑圣母，引进桃源洞，将瑞鹤二"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙，许配我兄弟二人为婚。成亲七日以后，别过仙姑归家。盼望天色尚早，就"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此前行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟双双上帝京，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.2857,
        0.5714,
        0.1429,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘子",
        "刘孙",
        "刘晨",
        "刘曾孙",
        "夫人",
        "康宁",
        "永庆",
        "老旦"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃刘府管家康宁是也。只因我家太老爷，出将入相，上朝未归，只得府门伺"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘晨上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观不尽奇花美景，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一时行到自家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁好像康宁，怎么这等年迈了。是与不是，待吾冒叫一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！那旁坐的，敢是康宁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，你是何人，敢叫吾康宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是你主人刘晨回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说。我家太老爷，去有七十余年，哪还象你这样白面书生。休得乱道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若不信，现有传家之宝玉虎坠，拿去看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，果然是太老爷回来了。小人叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来。太夫人呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在后堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请出堂来相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，永庆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（永庆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请太夫人出堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请太夫人出堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老旦上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老旦",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "光阴容易催人老，两鬓斑白似银条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老旦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜太夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何喜事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太老爷回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你家老爷回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，康宁过来。想你家太老爷去有七十余年，岂是这等白面书生？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太夫人不信，现有玉虎坠为证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，当真是你太老爷回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨、夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，（夫人）（相公）吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同哭相思） 幼年夫妇两离分，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到今日七十有余春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "康宁叩见太老爷、太夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "永庆叩见太老爷、太夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨、夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁、永庆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷可把以往之事，说来妾身一听？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人听来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟双双到汴京，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩蒙圣主点头名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瑞鹤二仙配为婚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "游山玩景虎冲散"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "游山玩景虎冲散"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想夫君终日常忧闷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜得今日转回家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝罢归来喜盈盈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见书生坐中厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迎接太老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "康宁，那是何人，敢与太夫人同坐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那就是去了七十余载的太老爷回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过一边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲在上，孩儿拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，这就是你爹爹回来了，向前见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹在上，孩儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘子妇上，刘子、刘子妇同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消。起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘孙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "簪缨世代，阀阅家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，孩儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。见过你祖父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，这就是祖父，待孙儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘孙妇上，刘孙、刘孙妇同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消拜了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢祖父。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘曾孙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘曾孙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鳌头独占先，宫花插鬓边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘曾孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，孩儿拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。见过你曾祖父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘曾孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘曾孙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾祖父在上，待曾孙儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘曾孙妇上，刘曾孙、刘曾孙妇同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消拜了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，自我去后，康宁、永庆，可曾定配花烛？"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自相公去后，妾身终日忧闷，未曾与他们完婚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官今日回来，和夫人当面与他二人完成花烛，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷言得极是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "康宁，永庆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁、永庆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自你太老爷去后，耽误你二人佳期。今日当着你太老爷太夫人之面，你二人拜"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "完花烛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁、永庆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，小人若大年纪，还拜什么花烛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是一百岁，也要拜的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁、永庆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢太老爷、太夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来拜吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七十八来八十三，"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白发齐眉配姻缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好似前朝彭祖临凡世。"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好似庐山老母降下凡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二人同入洞房吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "永庆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦哟若大年纪，还入什么洞房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "康宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是千百年好事，不要装腔，随我来吓。哈哈，丢丑了，丢丑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（康宁、永庆同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官今日回来，与夫人相会一面，我要上朝献丹展帕，还要入山修炼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，你看儿孙满堂，享不尽荣华富贵，还要入山修炼怎的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本当不去，犹恐有误仙子之言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要效张良去修仙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻恩爱重如山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘晨",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日洞中遇仙子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世上不觉七十年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘孙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焚香答谢天地德，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘子、刘子妇",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世代缨冠荣无边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
